ca.utoronto.utm.paint

类 Circle

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • ca.utoronto.utm.paint.Shape
        • ca.utoronto.utm.paint.Circle

  • public class Circle
extends Shape
    Subclass of Shape, which creates a circle centered at first click, with radius of distance from first click to the last Point clicked.
    作者:
    Haoran Xiao

              java.lang.Boolean outlined,
              int thickness,
              javafx.scene.paint.Color outlineColor)
        Another circle object constructor
        参数:
        start - centre of the circle
        color - color that the circle will be
        stroke - strokeType of the circle
        fill - whether the circle is filled or not
        outlined - whether the circle is outlined or not
        thickness - thickness of the stroke of a circle
        outlineColor - outline color of the circle
